      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, ¶ 18 April 1874. ¶ His Excellency ¶ the Minister of State of the Royal House ¶ and for Foreign Affairs...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">74.04.18c</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Adolph von Pfretzschner</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Ordensakten 5210, Bayerisches Hauptstaatsarchiv, Munich.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Melbourne,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">am 18. April 1874.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Sr. Excellenz</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">dem Staatsminister des Königl. Hauses</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">und des Äussern</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">A. v. Pfretzschner, etc.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">zu München.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Excellenz</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es liegt mir die ehrenvolle Pflicht ob, den Empfang Ew. Excellenz Zuschrift vom 28 Januar d. J.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">des Jahres. </p>
               </note> ehrerbietig anzuerkennen, durch welche mir die Mittheilung geworden, dass Sr. Majestät der König von Baiern sich herabliess, mir allergnädigst die Ritterwürde des Verdienst-Ordens vom heiligen Michael zu ertheilen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Durch den würdigen Kaiserlich Deutschen Consul, Herrn Brahe, ist mir nebst dem Brevet gleichfalls die prachtvolle Ordensinsignie eingehändigt.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich nahe mich nun Ew. Excellenz mit der Bitte, Sr Majestät, Ihrem erhabenen Könige, meinen tiefgefühlten Dank für diese hohe Auszeichnung ausdrücken zu wollen und die Versicherung, dass diese Ehrenbezeugung von einem Königshause, das seit Generationen sich dem Streben der Wissenschaften so schützend erwies, mich dauernd ermuthigen werde, so lange mir die Vorsehung Kraft verleiht, auf dem Pfade der Naturforschung weiter zu dringen, und so auch den schönen Anstalten der Wissenschaft in Ihrem Königslande nützlich zu werden.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit tiefster Ehrerbietung</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">18 April 1874.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">His Excellency</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">the Minister of State of the Royal House</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">and for Foreign Affairs</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">A von Pfretzschner</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">in Munich.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Excellency,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is my honourable duty to respectfully acknowledge Your Excellency's letter of 28 January this year,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Adolph von Pfretzscher to M, 28 January 1874 (in this edition as 74-01-28a).</p>
               </note> by which I was informed, that His Majesty, the King of Bavaria, has most graciously deigned to bestow on me the title of a Knight of the Order of Merit of St Michael.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The magnificent insignia of the Order together with the certificate have been passed on to me by the worthy Imperial German Consul, Mr Brahe.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I now approach Your Excellency and beg that you will express to His Majesty, your august King, my deeply felt gratitude for this high distinction, and give my assurance that this honour from a Royal House that has been a proven patron of science for generations will constantly encourage me to press forward on the path of natural science for as long as Providence grants me strength, so that I may also become useful to the fine institutes of science in your Kingdom.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With deepest respect</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
